790
01:05:23,960 --> 01:05:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jesmo, jesmo, ja sam ponudil.

791
01:05:25,960 --> 01:05:27,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ti sebićan, ti samo o sebi razmišliš.

792
01:05:27,960 --> 01:05:28,960
