793
01:05:28,960 --> 01:05:31,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam me uhvatio.

794
01:05:31,960 --> 01:05:34,960
[SPEAKER_00] Rekao si da si čovjek sa integritetom.

795
01:05:34,960 --> 01:05:37,960
