847
01:11:03,960 --> 01:11:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je doslovno istina.

848
01:11:06,960 --> 01:11:07,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

849
01:11:07,960 --> 01:11:08,960
[SPEAKER_00] Točno to.

850
01:11:08,960 --> 01:11:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Točno to.

851
01:11:10,960 --> 01:11:17,960
[SPEAKER_00] Koje ti sad pitanje bilo?

852
01:11:17,960 --> 01:11:24,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ti možeš uopće sam za sebe zaključiti što je zapravo moguće?

853
01:11:24,960 --> 01:11:29,960
